Home Library 
Requirements

1.	I want to be able to search books by their title, author’s name, publisher’s name and by genre.
2.	Each book will have a unique ID number, and to help physically locate the book= a shelf number.
3.	There could be titles published by different publishers and in different years (=different editions treated as separate book items).
4.	Only one copy of each title exists in the Library.
5.	A book can have multiple authors.
6.	Family/ friends can borrow books and I would like to be able to monitor who borrows what book at what date and the return date.

7.  The Database will be stored on my personal laptop.
8.  DB Browser for SQLite will be used for accessing the DB.

